'''Purkina Fasoo''' kɛna [[Afrɩka tɛtʊ tɔm|Afrɩka‎]] nɛ wɩsɩ ɖɩɖʊyɛta ɛjaɖɛ naɖɩyɛ nɛ payaɣ- ɖooo lɛ se: Hooti Foltaa. Teŋgu tɔcɔɔ ɛjaɖɛ nɖɩ nɛ pɩta kpɛɛɛ. Wɩsɩ ɖɩɖʊyɛ nɛ hayɩ kɩŋ ɖɔɖɔ lɛ [[Maalii (Mali)|Malii]] ɛjaɖɛ wɛna kamaɣ yɔɔ; wɩsɩ ɖɩɖʊyɛ taa lɛ, [[Nizɛɛrɩ (Niger)|Nizɛɛrɩ]] ɛjaɖɛ nɛ yee hadɛ kɩŋ nɛ wɩsɩ ɖɩlɩyɛ taa kɔ yɔ, [[Peenɛɛ (Bénin)|Peenɛɛ]] ɛjaɖɛ. Purkina Fasoo nɛ hadɛ kiŋ lɛ, [[Togo|Togo]] nɛ [[Kana (Ghana)|Kana]] ajɛya wɛna piyele wɩsɩ ɖɩɖʊyɛ nɛ hadɛ kɩn lɛ, [[Kootidiivʊwarɩ (Côte d'Ivoire)|Kootidiivʊwarɩ]] tɛtʊ.
[
Purkina Fasoo tɛtʊ sɔsɔtʊ kɔyɔ [[Wagaadugu (Ouagadougou)|Wagaadugu]] nɛ tɩwɛ Purkina Fasoo tɛtʊ hɛkʊ taa. Ɛjaɖɛ ɖɩnɛ ɖɩwɛ [[Afrɩka tɛtʊ tɔm|Afrɩka‎]] ajɛya kpeekpe kpɛndɩɣ ŋgbɛyɛ taa nɛ [[Afrika Wɩsɩɖʋɖʋyɛ Ajɛyɛ Tɔsʋʋ Ŋgbɛyɛ (CEDEAO)|CEDEAO]] ñɩnɖɩ taa. Keteŋga kpeekpe taa lɛ, yee pakpaɣ ajɛya hiu wena akɩla kʊñɔŋ taa wɛʊ kɔyɔ, pana ɖɔɖɔ Purkina Fasoo. 

Ɖooo lɛ, [[Fransɩɩ (France)|Fransɩɩ]] ɛjaɖɛ kakpacayaɣna-ɖɩ picɔ ɖɩkɔɔ ɖɩhiu ɖɩ-tɩ yɔɔ wɛʊ kɛ pɩnaɣ 1960. Papaazɩɣ yaʊ se Purkina Fasoo yɔ pideleɖi; [[Thomas Sankara|Thomas Sankara]] kewiyaɣ taa kɛ papɩsɩnaa mbʊ kɩyɛna fenaɣ nanza pɩnaɣ 1984. 

Ŋ̃ʊndɩna mba peɖiya Purkina Fasoo ɛjaɖɛ pɩkɔɔ pɩsɩɩna sɔnɔ yɔ, mba yɔ: [[Maurice Yaméaogo]] (1960-1966), [[Wp/kpb/Sangoulé Lamizana|Sangoulé Lamizana]] (1966 1980 ), [[Wp/kpb/Saye Zerbo|Saye Zerbo]] (1980 to 7 Kamɩŋ fenaɣ 1982), [[Wp/kpb/Jean-Baptiste Ouédraogo|Jean-Baptiste Ouédraogo]] (1982 to 11 Kamɩŋ fenaɣ 1983), [[Thomas Sankara|Thomas Sankara]] (1983—1987), [[Wp/kpb/Blaise Compaoré|Blaise Compaoré]] (1987-2014), [[Wp/kpb/Honoré Traoré|Honoré Traoré]], ɛkɛna [[Wp/kpb/Blaise Compaoré|Blaise Compaoré]] lone taa caɣyʊ nɛ fenasi naalɛ ɖeke ɛlaba nɛ [[Wp/kpb/Yacouba Isaac Zida|Yacouba Isaac Zida]] ñakpaɣ nɛ ɛlɛ la kɔzɔɖɔna naalɛ nɛ eyebina [[Wp/kpb/Michel Kafando|Michel Kafando]], [[Wp/kpb/Gilbert Diendéré|Gilbert Diendéré]]. Kpana salaŋ fenaɣ 2015 nɛ nnsɩɩna saŋayɩŋ fenaɣ 2015 ɖɔɖɔ lɛ, ɛnʊ cɔŋna ɛjaɖɛ nɖɩ ɖɩ-yɔɔ nɛ pɔtɔ caca nɛ palɩzɩ weyi lɛ, ɛɛkɛ Purkina Fasoo ñʊʊdʊ.

